# DDD Radar — English artifact descriptions
radar.CreditBalanceEntity.desc=The root entity for credit balance. Contains CreditBalanceState with balance, reserved, and incoming fields. Defines the CreditBalanceEvent sealed trait hierarchy.
radar.CreditBalanceEntity.constraint=Must only change state by applying events. All 7 event types must be handled exhaustively.
radar.Money.desc=Immutable value object representing a monetary amount. Enforces precision and currency constraints.
radar.Money.constraint=Must be immutable. Equality based on value, not identity. No setters or mutable fields.
radar.CreditBalanceEventHandler.desc=Pure function (State, Event) => State that applies domain events to evolve the CreditBalanceState.
radar.CreditBalanceEventHandler.constraint=Must be a pure function with no side effects. Pattern match must be exhaustive over all 7 event types.
radar.DepositRule.desc=Validates deposit commands: ensures the deposit amount is positive.
radar.DepositRule.constraint=Stateless pure function: (State, Money) => Either[iMadzError, List[CreditBalanceEvent]].
radar.WithdrawRule.desc=Validates withdrawal: ensures sufficient balance and positive amount.
radar.WithdrawRule.constraint=Must check balance >= amount before emitting BalanceChanged. Negative amounts are rejected.
radar.DeductFundsRule.desc=Validates fund deduction during Saga prepare phase. Ensures funds are reserved before deducting.
radar.DeductFundsRule.constraint=Must verify that reservation exists before allowing deduction. Part of Saga TCC flow.
radar.ReserveFundsRule.desc=Manages fund reservation during Saga prepare. Prevents double-reservation.
radar.ReserveFundsRule.constraint=Must check for existing reservation to prevent double-booking.
radar.AddInitialOnlyOnceRule.desc=Ensures credit balance can only be initialized once for a given account.
radar.AddInitialOnlyOnceRule.constraint=Must reject initialization if balance already exists. Enforces idempotent account creation.
radar.TransferDomainService.desc=Domain service coordinating balance transfer logic between two accounts.
radar.TransferDomainService.constraint=Must not depend on infrastructure. Should orchestrate entities and value objects.
radar.CreditBalanceAggregate.desc=Cluster-sharded aggregate root wrapping CreditBalanceEntity. Serializes commands into events via Akka EventSourcedBehavior.
radar.CreditBalanceAggregate.constraint=Must only change state by applying events. Commands validated against invariants before emitting events.
radar.CreditBalanceBehaviors.desc=Command handler functions handling Deposit, Withdraw, ReserveFunds, DeductFunds, ReleaseReservation commands.
radar.CreditBalanceBehaviors.constraint=Must use Either for error handling. Uses replyWithAndPublish pattern.
radar.CreditBalanceAggregateFactory.desc=Factory for creating CreditBalanceAggregate instances with proper initialization.
radar.CreditBalanceAggregateFactory.constraint=Must ensure aggregate is properly initialized with EventSourcedBehavior before use.
radar.CreditBalanceRepository.desc=Repository interface for accessing credit balance aggregates.
radar.CreditBalanceRepository.constraint=Interface only — no implementation details. Must return EntityRef for cluster-sharded access.
radar.CreditBalanceRepositoryImpl.desc=Implementation using Akka Cluster Sharding to locate aggregate entities.
radar.CreditBalanceRepositoryImpl.constraint=Must delegate to Akka sharding entityRef. No direct database access.
radar.credits_proto.desc=Protobuf schema for CreditBalanceState and all domain event types. Used for Akka Persistence serialization.
radar.credits_proto.constraint=Must stay in sync with Scala case classes (three-piece rule). Never remove fields.
radar.DepositService.desc=Handles deposit use case: validates input, loads aggregate, sends Deposit command.
radar.DepositService.constraint=Must not contain domain logic — delegates to aggregate. Orchestrates the use case flow.
radar.WithdrawService.desc=Handles withdrawal use case with balance validation.
radar.WithdrawService.constraint=Must not contain domain logic — delegates to aggregate invariants.
radar.MoneyTransferService.desc=Initiates money transfer Saga by creating a SagaTransactionCoordinator entity.
radar.MoneyTransferService.constraint=Must create coordinator with correct step definitions.
radar.GetBalanceQuery.desc=Queries current balance from the aggregate via cluster sharding.
radar.GetBalanceQuery.constraint=Reads from write-side aggregate (not read model). Use only when up-to-date balance is required.
radar.IncomeExpenseReport.desc=Queries the read-side MySQL database for the last 12 months of income and expense summaries.
radar.IncomeExpenseReport.constraint=Must query read model only (MySQL/ScalikeJDBC). Never access event journal directly.
radar.MonthlySummaryProjection.desc=Akka Projection definition for building the monthly summary read model from domain events.
radar.MonthlySummaryProjection.constraint=Must be idempotent — handle redelivered events gracefully. Uses at-least-once delivery.
radar.MonthlySummaryHandler.desc=Event handler that transforms domain events into MySQL read model rows via ETL logic.
radar.MonthlySummaryHandler.constraint=Must handle all relevant event types. Updates to read model must be idempotent.
radar.MonthlySummaryRepoTrait.desc=Repository interface for the monthly summary projection read model.
radar.MonthlySummaryRepoTrait.constraint=Interface only. Defines CRUD operations on the read model without implementation details.
radar.MonthlySummaryRepoImpl.desc=ScalikeJDBC implementation of the monthly summary repository.
radar.MonthlySummaryRepoImpl.constraint=Must use ScalikeJDBC for MySQL access. Only executes read-side queries.
radar.MonthlyProjectionBootstrap.desc=Bootstraps the Akka Projection: registers projection with the event journal and starts processing.
radar.MonthlyProjectionBootstrap.constraint=Must register with Akka Projection system. Defines source provider and handler binding.
radar.MoneyTransferSagaTransactor.desc=Saga transaction coordinator for money transfers. Orchestrates Prepare → Commit → Compensate phases.
radar.MoneyTransferSagaTransactor.constraint=Must handle distributed timeouts. Compensate only successfully-prepared steps.
radar.SagaTransactorBehaviors.desc=Command handler for the Saga transactor. Processes transaction lifecycle commands.
radar.SagaTransactorBehaviors.constraint=Must follow backward recovery pattern. Phase transitions must be atomic and persistent.
radar.SagaParticipant.desc=Trait defining the Saga participant interface: doPrepare, doCommit, doCompensate.
radar.SagaParticipant.constraint=Each operation must be idempotent. Participants must not have side effects outside their domain.
radar.saga_participant_proto.desc=Protobuf schema for serializing saga participant state.
radar.saga_participant_proto.constraint=Must follow the three-piece rule with Scala case class and Proto Converter.
radar.saga_v2_proto.desc=Protobuf schema for SagaTransactionCoordinator state and events.
radar.saga_v2_proto.constraint=Must maintain backward compatibility. New fields are append-only.
radar.TxCoordinatorRepoTrait.desc=Repository interface for saga transaction coordinators.
radar.TxCoordinatorRepoTrait.constraint=Interface only — defines find/load operations for coordinator persistence IDs.
radar.TxCoordinatorRepoImpl.desc=Implementation of the transaction coordinator repository using Akka Persistence.
radar.TxCoordinatorRepoImpl.constraint=Must use Akka Persistence Query for reading events. Writes go through the coordinator entity.
radar.SagaSerializer.desc=Serializes and deserializes Saga domain objects to/from Protobuf for persistence.
radar.SagaSerializer.constraint=Must handle all saga event types. Serialization errors must fail fast with clear messages.
radar.CreditBalanceBootstrap.desc=Bootstraps the CreditBalanceAggregate: initializes Akka Cluster Sharding for the aggregate entity.
radar.CreditBalanceBootstrap.constraint=Must register entity type key with ClusterSharding. Configures shards and passivation.
radar.SagaTxCoordinatorBootstrap.desc=Bootstraps the Saga coordinator entity with Cluster Sharding.
radar.SagaTxCoordinatorBootstrap.constraint=Must register the Saga-MoneyTransfer entity type key. Passivation must not drop in-progress transactions.
radar.CreditBalanceEventAdapter.desc=Converts domain events to/from Protobuf for MongoDB journal storage.
radar.CreditBalanceEventAdapter.constraint=Must handle all event types with explicit pattern matching.
radar.SagaEventAdapter.desc=Converts Saga transaction events to/from Protobuf. Renames old event types for backward compatibility.
radar.SagaEventAdapter.constraint=Must handle event type renaming for schema evolution. Part of the three-piece rule compliance.
radar.StepExecutorEventAdapter.desc=Converts step executor events (per-step saga progress) to/from Protobuf.
radar.StepExecutorEventAdapter.constraint=Must serialize step state including retry count, phase, and error details.
radar.CreditBalanceSnapshotAdapter.desc=Converts CreditBalanceState snapshots to/from Protobuf for faster aggregate recovery.
radar.CreditBalanceSnapshotAdapter.constraint=Snapshots must be backwards-compatible. Older snapshot versions must still be readable.
radar.HomeController.desc=Play Framework controller for index page, deposit, withdraw, and transfer REST endpoints.
radar.HomeController.constraint=Must delegate to ApplicationServices — no domain logic in controller. Validates HTTP input.
radar.ShowcaseController.desc=Serves the Saga Showcase SPA, Saga WebSocket event stream, and all /api/saga/* endpoints.
radar.ShowcaseController.constraint=WebSocket must use BroadcastHub for fan-out. Event bridge subscribes to Akka event stream.
radar.DddGuideController.desc=Serves DDD Guide and Projection Showcase pages plus /api/projection/status and /api/aggregate/balances.
radar.DddGuideController.constraint=API endpoints must query read model only. Balance query goes through aggregate (write side).

# New artifacts — Domain Layer
radar.MoneyTransferTransactionEntity.desc=Domain entity for money transfer transactions. Contains state (New/Initiated/Prepared/Completed/Failed) and events for the transfer lifecycle.
radar.MoneyTransferTransactionEntity.constraint=State changes only via applyEvent. Status transitions must be valid (Idempotent state machine).
radar.CancelIncomingCreditRule.desc=Handles cancellation of incoming credits during Saga compensation. Removes the pending transfer from incoming credits.
radar.CancelIncomingCreditRule.constraint=Must handle both Prepare compensation (discard) and Commit compensation (cannot reverse without amount). Idempotent if credit already cleared.
radar.CommitIncomingCreditsRule.desc=Commits previously recorded incoming credits to the account balance during Saga Commit phase.
radar.CommitIncomingCreditsRule.constraint=Must verify incomingCredits entry exists before committing. Rejects if already committed or not found.
radar.InitiateTransactionRule.desc=Validates the initiation of a money transfer transaction. Checks status is New and amount is positive.
radar.InitiateTransactionRule.constraint=Must guard against duplicate initiation. Validates amount > 0.
radar.RecordIncomingCreditsRule.desc=Records an incoming credit transfer from the sender during Saga Prepare phase. Adds to incomingCredits map.
radar.RecordIncomingCreditsRule.constraint=Must verify transfer is not already recorded. Balance unchanged at this stage (deferred to Commit).
radar.ReleaseReservedFundsRule.desc=Releases previously reserved funds during Saga compensation or after deduction completion.
radar.ReleaseReservedFundsRule.constraint=Must verify reservation exists before releasing. Handles both Prepare and Commit compensation scenarios.

# New artifacts — Application Layer
radar.CreditBalanceProtocol.desc=Protocol definition: commands (Deposit, Withdraw, ReserveFunds, etc.), reply types, and CommandHandler type alias for the CreditBalance aggregate.
radar.CreditBalanceProtocol.constraint=All commands and replies must extend CborSerializable. Type alias defines Effect-based handler signature.
radar.CreditBalanceCommandHelpers.desc=Helper traits providing command-to-event mapping logic for CreditBalanceBehaviors (DepositHelper, WithdrawHelper, etc.).
radar.CreditBalanceCommandHelpers.constraint=Each helper maps a validated command to its corresponding domain event. Pure functions only.
radar.SagaProgressEvent.desc=Sealed trait hierarchy for all Saga progress events emitted via WebSocket (TransactionStarted, StepOngoing, StepCompleted, etc.).
radar.SagaProgressEvent.constraint=Events must be serializable to JSON for WebSocket broadcast. Used by ShowcaseController for real-time UI updates.
radar.CreateCreditBalanceService.desc=Application service for creating (initializing) a new credit balance account with an initial deposit.
radar.CreateCreditBalanceService.constraint=Must check account doesn't exist before creating. Delegates to AddInitialOnlyOnceRule via aggregate.
radar.DynamicShowcaseParticipant.desc=Configurable Saga participant for the showcase demo. Supports injection of Success, FailRetryable, FailNonRetryable, Timeout, FailTwiceThenSucceed behaviors.
radar.DynamicShowcaseParticipant.constraint=Behavior state is stored in ConcurrentHashMap keyed by stepId. Reset between demo runs.
radar.FromAccountParticipant.desc=Saga participant for the sender account: reserves funds (Prepare), deducts (Commit), or releases (Compensate).
radar.FromAccountParticipant.constraint=Each phase must be idempotent. Compensate must handle both Prepare and Commit compensation correctly.
radar.ToAccountParticipant.desc=Saga participant for the receiver account: records incoming credits (Prepare), commits (Commit), or cancels (Compensate).
radar.ToAccountParticipant.constraint=Each phase must be idempotent. Commit and Cancel rely on recorded state from Prepare.
radar.MoneyTransferContext.desc=Context object holding shared state for the money transfer Saga (sender/receiver user IDs, amount, Repository references).
radar.MoneyTransferContext.constraint=Must be immutable after construction. Passed to all Saga participants for the transfer.
radar.MoneyTransferProtocol.desc=Protocol definition for the MoneyTransferTransaction aggregate: commands (Initiate, UpdateStatus, AdminManualFix, AdminResume).
radar.MoneyTransferProtocol.constraint=All commands must extend CborSerializable. Reply types must include error channels for failure handling.
radar.MoneyTransferTransactionRepository.desc=Repository interface for accessing MoneyTransferTransaction entities. Returns EntityRef for the transfer Saga coordinator.
radar.MoneyTransferTransactionRepository.constraint=Interface only. Implementation uses Akka Cluster Sharding for entity location.

# New artifacts — Infrastructure Layer
radar.ApplicationBootstrap.desc=Top-level bootstrap that wires all aggregates, projections, and Sagas together at application startup.
radar.ApplicationBootstrap.constraint=Must initialize CreditBalance aggregate, Saga coordinator, and Monthly projection in correct dependency order.
radar.TransactionBootstrap.desc=Bootstraps the MoneyTransferTransaction aggregate entity with Cluster Sharding.
radar.TransactionBootstrap.constraint=Must register the MoneyTransferTransaction entity type key. Configures EventSourcedBehavior with TransactionEventAdapter and TransactionSnapshotAdapter.
radar.CreditBalanceProtoConverters.desc=Converter trait providing toProto/fromProto methods for all CreditBalance domain events and state to Protobuf format.
radar.CreditBalanceProtoConverters.constraint=Must have explicit converters for all 7 event types. Used by CreditBalanceEventAdapter and CreditBalanceSnapshotAdapter.
radar.SagaProtoConverters.desc=Converter trait for Saga-related Protobuf conversions in the main app module.
radar.SagaProtoConverters.constraint=Must handle serialization of Saga step definitions and participant references.
radar.TransactionEventAdapter.desc=Converts MoneyTransferTransaction events (TransactionInitiated, Prepared, Completed, Failed) to/from Protobuf.
radar.TransactionEventAdapter.constraint=Must handle all 4 event types. Part of the three-piece rule for transfer transaction persistence.
radar.TransactionSnapshotAdapter.desc=Converts MoneyTransferTransactionState snapshots to/from Protobuf for faster aggregate recovery.
radar.TransactionSnapshotAdapter.constraint=Must handle all Status enum variants (New, Initiated, Prepared, Completed, Failed).
radar.TransactionSerializationStrategies.desc=Serialization strategy definitions for transaction-related Protobuf types in the Akka serialization system.
radar.TransactionSerializationStrategies.constraint=Must register serialization bindings for all transaction Protobuf types.
radar.MoneyTransferTransactionRepositoryImpl.desc=Implementation of MoneyTransferTransactionRepository using Akka Cluster Sharding to locate transaction entities.
radar.MoneyTransferTransactionRepositoryImpl.constraint=Must delegate to sharding.entityRefFor with the MoneyTransferTransaction entity type key.
radar.SuffixCollectionNames.desc=Utility that generates MongoDB collection name suffixes for different event types in the journal.
radar.SuffixCollectionNames.constraint=Must produce consistent, deterministic suffixes for journal collection separation.
radar.BootstrapModule.desc=Guice module that binds all application services, repositories, and bootstrap components for dependency injection.
radar.BootstrapModule.constraint=Must configure all bindings at startup. Enables Play''s compile-time DI for the entire application.
